  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  This is Nami (<a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E6%B3%A2">æ³¢</a>), a library for parallel wavelet compression and encoding.

  <h2>Author</h2>
  Nami was implemented by Todd Gamblin at 
  <a href="http://www.llnl.gov">Lawrence Livermore National Laboratory</a>.

  Please send questions, bug reports, or suggestions 
  to <a href="mailto:tgamblin@llnl.gov">tgamblin@llnl.gov</a>.

